                <p>正文233页写的是紫苑（yuan）</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p43248090-3.jpg"></div></div><p>正文262页写的也是紫苑（yuan）（索引标为270，实际出现在269末行）</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p43248090-1.jpg"></div></div><p>正文275页写的是紫菀（wan）</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p43248090-4.jpg"></div></div><p>植物名称词汇表290页写的是紫菀（wan）</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p43248090-5.jpg"></div></div><p>索引315页又变成了紫苑（yuan）</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p43248090-2.jpg"></div></div><p>这翻译也太不稳定了吧。。。。。。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







